  <summary date="2023-08-20T20:41:39Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Technology Grants to Strengthen Domestic Mining Education Act of 2022 or the Mining Schools Act of 2022

This bill establishes a grant program for mining schools to recruit students and enhance educational programs, including those related to critical mineral and rare earth element exploration, extraction, and refining.</summary>
